data.title: Manish Gupta Movies and Shows
data.meta_description: Learn about Manish Gupta on Apple TV. Browse shows and movies that feature Manish Gupta including Sarkar and The Stoneman Murders.
data.text: Manish Gupta is a film director and writer in the Indian film industry. As a director, Manish has directed the movies One Friday Night, 420 IPC, Rahasya, Hostel, The Stoneman Murders and Darna Zaroori Hai. As a writer, Manish has written the screenplay and dialogues for the movies Sarkar and Section 375.
